title: Someone Spills The Tea On Lunchbox + Girl Group Discusses If You Should Use A Baby Name Suggested By An Ex
itunes:title: Someone Spills The Tea On Lunchbox + Girl Group Discusses If You Should Use A Baby Name Suggested By An Ex
description:
Someone had some tea to spill on Lunchbox. The Girl Group discusses if it’s ok to name your child a name if it was originally suggested by an ex. Also, Amy talks about wanting to get Bobby a dog for his upcoming birthday.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
